ygData.messageBody:
Hello all!

I have been very busy in Kunark lately and need some help with some
odd items I have found.
Looking to see if there are quests, recipes, skills that use these
items so I can either sell them or give them to someone who can use
them (and they sure are filling up in the bank!)

*denotes a foraged item

Froglok Escort Fife
*Petrified Redwood
Busted Froglok Slave Shackles
Forsaken Pariah Mask
Ticket Stub
Lens of Sorts
*Craked Shell
*Hopeless Willow Moss
*Cursed Clover of Viesarif I eat this does my charisma go down
or
something?
*Maneater Bud
*Wild Radish
*Wild Cabbage
Rhino Hoof
Sarnak Blood

Thanks in advance for any help on these

Teaa
Cazic-Thule
